<!-- Basic Auth -->
<h2 id="basic-auth">Basic Auth</h2>
<a class="badge post">POST</a> /authenticate

```javascript
// request example
{
   "email": "{email}",
   "password": "{password}"
}
```
|Parameter|Value|
|----|----|
|Email|Registered email|
|Password|Password|



```javascript
// response example
{
   status: 200,
   data: {
      auth_token: "{auth_token}",
      api_key: "{api_key}"
   }
}
```
|Parameter|Value|
|----|----|
|auth_token|Token provided by Transfez for each authorized user|
|api_key|Required for every other request made to Transfez API services|

<!-- End Basic Auth -->
